'''Multiple myeloma''' is a type of [[cancer]] involving the [[plasma cells]]. Some symptoms of the multiple myeloma are [[bone pain]], [[renal failure]], recurring infections and [[anemia]]. It is treated with [[chemotherapy]]. A commonly used chemotherapy regimen is the Vincristine, Adriamycin, and Dexamethasone. [[Thalidomide]]s, [[velcade]]s, [[melphalan]]s, prednisones and interferons have also been used.

